articles.title: Caitlin Clark explodes for 32 points in return from injury as Indiana Fever hand New York Liberty first loss of season - CNN
articles.description: Caitlin Clark scored a season-high 32 points and equaled a career-high seven three-pointers on her return from injury as the Indiana Fever defeated the New York Liberty 102-88 on Saturday.
